title: NFL ATL:  Week 2 TNF preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL:  Week 2 TNF preview
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling give you their biggest Week 1 takeaways and preview the Week 2 “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the New York Jets and New England Patriots. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL .
